Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.20,0:00:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.54,0:00:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.20,0:00:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta go! Don't let\Nthis opportunity slip by!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.74,0:00:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To think I'd be in such a situation!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.40,0:00:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My life, led lacking all splendor, is heading\Ntoward a climax surrounded by three women!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.21,0:00:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.92,0:00:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Unless I aim to become some Renaissance man\Nof the sexual arts, I must decide on one of them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.33,0:00:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And obviously that's the\None with a real body, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.04,0:00:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hanuki-san is a woman with no\Nfaults on an emotional or visual level,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.33,0:00:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but tonight she was just too... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.75,0:00:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit it with the pretentious\Nmonologues already!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.50,0:00:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let your feelings guide your body!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.41,0:00:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Carry me away...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.95,0:00:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaori-san is a silent, lovely maiden.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.79,0:00:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, we are fated to be apart!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.83,0:00:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! I know already, sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we are not able to meet, then\NI cannot continue this relationship any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.41,0:00:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keiko-san is classy and ladylike,\Nbut I can't see her like that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.54,0:01:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true, sure... In this situation\Nthere's only one choice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.37,0:01:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.58,0:01:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.16,0:01:08.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The Tatami Galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then I was a brand-spanking\Nnew freshman university student{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.33,0:02:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and before my eyes were open innumerable\Ndoors to that rose-colored campus life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.66,0:02:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, devoting my life to a single circle{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.00,0:02:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}poses a chance of wasting\Nmy entire college life in vain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.20,0:02:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One must spread out the risk! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.68,0:02:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will join many circles and experience\Na diversified rose-colored campus life!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.83,0:02:53.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,English Conversation Circle
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.60,0:02:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I bet I could take trips abroad\Nas easily as going to Awaji Island.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:02:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Able to read English newspapers,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.09,0:03:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I would no longer be forced to\Ndance only to Japanese language news.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Among the large number of native languages,\Nit's the one spoken by most people.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.82,0:03:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}English! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.89,0:03:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Able to converse with anyone... Able\Nto make acquaintances with foreigners...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And most of all, not encumbered by Japanese's\Narrogant sense of shame or enlarged self-pride,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}with English conversation I can have a buoyant\Ntalk session with a raven-haired maiden.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.20,0:03:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no down-side to learning that skill!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.75,0:03:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is difficult... Conversing in\NEnglish like this is a tough road to travel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Here we go again... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As I put the grammar together in my head,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.95,0:03:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}improving and polishing the thought,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.54,0:03:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the conversation has already\Nproceeded to the next stage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn, I'm taking this way too seriously.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, if the other choice is spouting\Nsome grammatically incorrect English,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.16,0:03:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take pride in being a man of few words!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silent as usual, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.04,0:03:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't say anything, it's your loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.12,0:03:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have plenty of English\Nvocabulary in my head, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.28,0:04:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should just go with your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.25,0:04:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hanuki-san's English was left\Na bit too much to her feelings,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.75,0:04:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and to be honest, it's a miracle the\Ninstructor understood a thing she said.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.10,0:04:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was speaking from the soul\Nwhich I myself could never hope to do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.81,0:04:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hanuki-san is a dental hygienist,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and she spoke passionately about\Nher work and knowledge of teeth,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.70,0:04:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}raising everyone in the circle's dental IQ.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And among her talks, the badmouthing\Nof "Sexual Harassment Dentist Kubouzuka"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.56,0:04:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}was most acclaimed. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.32,0:04:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She and I had a common acquaintance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.87,0:04:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you and Ozu-{\i1}kun {\i0}are in the same year?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.20,0:04:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a small world, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.87,0:04:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a patient at our practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I think he's about to be fixed up,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.54,0:04:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he reverts back, so he never completely heals.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.83,0:04:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suspect it is just a plot by him to\Nkeep tasting your fingers, Hanuki-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.50,0:04:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's always thinking up cunning plots like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.64,0:04:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's his hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.16,0:04:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He lives for messing with other people's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.53,0:05:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozu and I are in the same year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite being in the electrical\Nengineering department,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.37,0:05:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he hates both electricity and\Nelectronics, as well as engineering.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I first met him in June of our freshman year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, might you be troubled?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.73,0:05:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a devil who wants\Nto bargain away my soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You say some pretty mean things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.86,0:05:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to support you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,College life is super-busy\Nwith searching for love.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.66,0:05:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it might help to lower the\Nburden of your academic study,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.29,0:05:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we have prepared reports for most occasions...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, make use of them to fully\Nexperience this abundant campus life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.29,0:05:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're holding a sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.64,0:05:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, juggling three clubs at once,\Nand pressured by school work,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.16,0:05:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was easily cajoled by Ozu's wheedling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.68,0:05:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The organization known as the\N"Print Shop" creates forged reports,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I had fallen into a situation where\NI was dependent on them to get me out of jams.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.19,0:05:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hence, my inability to break off my\Nrelationship with him I so despised.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozu is nothing but trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.91,0:05:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like he has underhanded\Ndealings in a bunch of other circles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't rest unless discord is\Nringing out from all around him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.41,0:06:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that if he wasn't here,\NI would have led a better life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, he pisses me off...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.79,0:06:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're so worked up about it,\Nwhy don't you talk about it in English?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.09,0:06:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,English is all about feeling, so with\Nthat much passion grammar is secondary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:14.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,OZ News Episode 1
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And thus my OZ News became a well-known\Nevent in the English conversation circle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.54,0:06:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OZ news is going great, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to you, Hanuki-{\i1}san{\i0}.\NOzu's evil deeds know no cultural boundaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.72,0:06:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Around this time Hanuki-san and I would\Nalways go to a cafe after the circle meeting.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.41,0:06:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanuki-{\i1}san{\i0}, do you drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.22,0:06:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.93,0:06:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can cause problems, though,\Nso I only drink with people I'm close to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Close to? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.29,0:06:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eww! It's Kubouzuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:07:00.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in the hotel lounge right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:07:00.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to come for a drink? (^_-)~☆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.76,0:07:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess those speeches \Nweren't all exaggeration.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell no. That perverted dentist has a wife\Nand kids, and he's still doing this every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.45,0:07:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.72,0:07:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should quit and sue his ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.00,0:07:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I'll handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.00,0:07:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanuki-{\i1}san{\i0}, do you have a boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.37,0:07:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether we're going out or not...\NIt's a love-hate relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he like?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's been totally neglecting me,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.25,0:07:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so if it's like this, maybe I'd rather\Nhave some guy that asks me out every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.04,0:07:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I'm always being\Ndragged around by Ozu, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.18,0:07:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah? I hear you've been exchanging letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just a hobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm trying to add some\Nextra flavor to my campus life or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Ozu really tell you all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That evil bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.67,0:07:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Ozu can be very devoted as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't seem that way to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.70,0:07:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.91,0:07:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't heard about Ozu-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s love?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His love?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozu-{\i1}kun {\i0}is in love with someone right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.67,0:08:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His partner has led a sheltered life,\Nso he's having quite a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.68,0:08:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He told me to keep it a secret, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For someone like him? No way in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.12,0:08:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry. Going to a "mystery hotpot."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.77,0:08:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With "him."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.29,0:08:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.16,0:08:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.62,0:08:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So, dear viewers, be not surprised!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.99,0:08:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have been living these past few weeks with\Nthis woman, Kaori-san, after some happenings.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Those of you who see a\Nlove-doll as nothing more{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}than a device to manage one's\Nsexual desires will not understand,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.38,0:08:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but this is extremely sophisticated taste.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:47.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Aiming to become an international actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.68,0:08:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Today I taught English conversation again."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Although the longest I've\Nstudied abroad is in Paris,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.87,0:08:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my experience is of great\Nvalue to everyone who has not."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And furthermore, I had been exchanging letters{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.83,0:08:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}with a girl after a certain\Npoint for these past two years.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.17,0:08:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her name is Higuchi Keiko-san,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and I can tell her intelligence\Nand education from her letters.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.03,0:09:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She is surely my ideal woman. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.72,0:09:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nothing much remarkable had\Nhappened to me prior to entering college.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.83,0:09:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And once I realized that, I found\Nmyself on the board of the game of "Love."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.85,0:09:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From now on I must continuously meet women,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}keep meticulous dates in my date book,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.29,0:09:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and whisper sweet nothings\Nuntil I start coughing up blood, yes?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just thinking about it made me dizzy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.04,0:09:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had to choose one eventually. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I was also happy as I was pondering it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, the situation took a sudden turn!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.09,0:09:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It may look like I was\Nturning things around well,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but everything started\Nsuddenly going out-of-gear!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.63,0:09:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is odd. Something is wrong.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.98,0:09:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her grammar! Her grammar is quite accurate!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's the matter? What happened to\Nher soulful speech overflowing with passion?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.41,0:09:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wanna go out for some drinks?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was finally asked out\Nfor a drink by Hanuki-san!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.25,0:09:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This certifies that she feels close to me now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.66,0:09:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.60,0:09:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a report I need to write today...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.84,0:10:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.06,0:10:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Good luck on your report!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.96,0:10:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is this okay? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.55,0:10:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You sure about this? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Letting Hanuki-san go like that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hanuki-san was clearly\Nnot acting like herself today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's been totally neglecting me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.84,0:10:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Perhaps something happened\Nbetween her and her boyfriend?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.91,0:10:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That would explain why\Nshe asked me out for drinks.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.16,0:10:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Perhaps Hanuki-san needed\Nsome emotional support?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.94,0:10:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Should not I, her cafe buddy of two years,\Nprovide support in her time of need?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But today is my last day with Kaori-san.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.44,0:10:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are being torn apart. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.09,0:10:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if you'll forget about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And also, I received this\Nletter from Keiko-san the other day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can wait no longer. I want to tell you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.41,0:10:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll be waiting at the Cafe Collection.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.58,0:10:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If perchance you do not come, let us no\Nlonger persist in this exchange of letters.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:10:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She is waiting tonight as well. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.91,0:11:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All my accounts from these past\Ntwo years are approaching settlement!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.69,0:11:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.62,0:11:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Before I realized it, I had come\Nto the fortune teller in Kiyamachi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.31,0:11:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are currently having difficulty\Nchoosing between three things,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.05,0:11:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but opportunity is always\Ndangling before your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.83,0:11:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be 6,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.60,0:11:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't answer a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.75,0:11:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So if it's like this, I'd rather have\Nsome guy that asks me out every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I knew it, I can't leave her be!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.05,0:11:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I cannot allow her to be ruined tonight\Nby some perverted dentist's invitation!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}First comes Hanuki-san!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanuki-{\i1}san{\i0}, don't let yourself\Nfall into Kubouzuka's clutches!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.82,0:11:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You? Why aren't you at your post?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.04,0:11:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jougasaki-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.66,0:11:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you! Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.70,0:11:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You two know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.70,0:11:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really understand, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, look at you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.89,0:11:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have high tolerance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.75,0:11:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured you'd be worthless at your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Is it time for a drinking contest?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.54,0:11:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drink, drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:11:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if you can\Nappreciate the taste of this wine?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.24,0:12:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And how many bottles will it take for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's how you want to play it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.78,0:12:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First one to collapse loses!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That goes without saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well I'm not giving in!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we move on to "Walker"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.43,0:12:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.76,0:12:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was a grand, manly\Nbattle between Jougasaki and I.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.08,0:12:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was starting to lose consciousness...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.03,0:12:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But Jougasaki also seemed close to losing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}By the way, Hanuki-san showed no\Nsigns of being done in by the alcohol.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's drink more!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.98,0:12:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was already at my limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.03,0:12:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.04,0:13:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanuki-{\i1}san{\i0}, don't fall for a man like Jougasaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.12,0:13:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have higher standards!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.18,0:13:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Jougasaki-{\i1}kun {\i0}and I aren't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.75,0:13:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just an old friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.45,0:13:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't think you'd come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.87,0:13:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's head to another place!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.21,0:13:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still want to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to finish that report and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.96,0:13:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go home already...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I don't hurry, Kaori-san will...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.41,0:13:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.37,0:13:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to hell and die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.34,0:13:44.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shimogamo Taxi
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanuki-{\i1}san{\i0}, your address!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakyou-ku Shimgamohigashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.81,0:13:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a castella, so spend the night...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.39,0:13:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to hurry, or Keiko-san will...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, try and walk straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is lookin' good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your room number?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.08,0:14:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.95,0:14:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kiddin'...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.37,0:14:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna check my mail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that can wait, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.57,0:14:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, that's what I'm talkin' about!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.62,0:14:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go, here we go, here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.12,0:14:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.14,0:14:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My once-in-a-lifetime chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.93,0:14:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even since I passed through\Nthat accursed gate of puberty,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my Johnny has been\Nforced into a miserable state.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.33,0:14:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed my history is nothing but\Nthe history of my Johnny's suppression.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For having a man like me\Nas your master... I apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight's the night!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will keep my pride as a civilized person!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.16,0:14:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.79,0:14:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is your key?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.04,0:14:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Uh... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:14:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? It won't go in...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.95,0:15:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.04,0:15:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it went in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.16,0:15:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to come in for some herb tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.54,0:15:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.08,0:15:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...don't mind if I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.44,0:15:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I think I drank too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.33,0:15:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice facing the river.\NKind of loud, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are we supposed to get through\Nthis situation in a chivalrous manner?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must retain our honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.11,0:15:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go! Yeehaw!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a seat on the sofa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.46,0:15:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait until it boils.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.47,0:15:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me read your palm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.75,0:15:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this one's totally separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.41,0:15:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means you can't\Ntell the situation you're in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.41,0:16:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it seems like you're suited to romance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.41,0:16:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes! Get this\Nparty started, heck yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let me see inside your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.58,0:16:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Hanuki-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.50,0:16:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a gum massage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one's on the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.20,0:16:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?\NWhy do you look so scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.08,0:16:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I always look like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.62,0:16:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You liar...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.75,0:16:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have a wrinkle there before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.70,0:16:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.45,0:16:25.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Frontal Lobe
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.17,0:16:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amygdala, situation report!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:36.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Amygdala
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Currently our pulse is elevated,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.66,0:16:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and sweating will not cease.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.83,0:16:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cause is from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.75,0:16:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two soft swells are pressing\Nagainst the mothership.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:40.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Cerebellum
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:40.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Parietal Lobe
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.79,0:16:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I tried to fend off such a situation calmly,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.00,0:16:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but as I'd suspected,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.00,0:16:42.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Occipital Lobe
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.00,0:16:42.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Temporal Lobe
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.00,0:16:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it was an extremely difficult task.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:45.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Frontal Lobe
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.58,0:16:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why is it that these soft swellings of no merit{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}have such control over us men? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was not able to solve that riddle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.41,0:16:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop being so pretentious!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.41,0:16:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think, feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.78,0:16:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Of course, considering the position\NHanuki-san's breasts are in right now,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.75,0:16:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I would not fault myself\Nfor becoming aroused...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.83,0:16:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're aroused?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.65,0:16:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to our pride?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:17:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I cannot allow these mere\Nswells to grab hold of my pure heart
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.08,0:17:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and sacrifice my long-protected,\Nunavoidable chastity!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My pride won't allow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.53,0:17:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so tense.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.34,0:17:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, they're all worn down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.33,0:17:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All you ever do is grind\Nyour teeth. You're so tense...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.87,0:17:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your gums are soft, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.04,0:17:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all pink and inexperienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.66,0:17:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it feel good right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.87,0:17:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to go deeper?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:41.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Succum
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:18:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take emergency shelter in the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.37,0:18:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.54,0:18:01.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bathroom
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:02.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Ack, it's a cockroach!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's a cockroach!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.62,0:18:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was our opportunity! Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.12,0:18:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.87,0:18:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.25,0:18:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.66,0:18:15.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can I be called civilized if I allow myself\Nto be controlled by my desires of the hour?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.00,0:18:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can I keep my pride taking advantage of a\Nwoman falling over from too much alcohol?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.00,0:18:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.91,0:18:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This situation came about unexpectedly,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so it was only now that\NI tried to think it through calmly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.37,0:18:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hanuki-san, Kaori-san, or Keiko-san?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The choice is obvious, you dolt!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.79,0:18:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was then that I thought of something.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.91,0:18:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could it be that Hanuki-san\Nactually wanted to be with me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.64,0:18:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.31,0:18:51.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Last Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.62,0:18:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's inexcusable to partner with someone
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.62,0:18:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you don't have a burning passion for
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.84,0:18:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,based purely on desire\Njust because you're lonely!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.25,0:18:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.50,0:18:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I despise this sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:18:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The door to a new world is opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:19:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to see what's on the other side?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.54,0:19:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I want to see! But now is not the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this isn't the opportunity, then when is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because this is an opportunity\Nthat I should wait for her to sober up
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.45,0:19:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before properly restarting \Nmerger negotiations!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.75,0:19:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.58,0:19:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been\Ncomplaining about my bad luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.25,0:19:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.54,0:19:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johnny, I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.83,0:19:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bonds between man and\Nwoman can't be tied so simply...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.04,0:19:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know... I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.54,0:19:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.58,0:19:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just have to wait some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.70,0:19:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's a little while longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.12,0:19:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johnny, you understand me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.15,0:19:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how much time had passed?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.16,0:19:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I came to, it\Nseemed like I had fallen asleep.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.41,0:19:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Has Hanuki-san calmed down by now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.16,0:19:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For some reason, Hanuki-san\Nlooks strangely like Ozu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.33,0:19:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh wait, that is Ozu. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.83,0:19:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:20:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try putting yourself in my shoes, being\Ncalled out by Hanuki-{\i1}san {\i0}or Jougasaki-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.75,0:20:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.79,0:20:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When she drinks, the wheels\Ncome off her reason a bit, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.70,0:20:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.41,0:20:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she, perhaps, lick your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.70,0:20:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.43,0:20:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has a bad habit of licking\Npeople's faces when she drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.04,0:20:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She refrains from going drinking\Nwith people she doesn't know well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.58,0:20:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But today she got carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, she'd like you to consider\Nwhat happened today water under the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.41,0:20:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.29,0:20:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't do anything, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.16,0:20:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I did was get my face licked.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.75,0:20:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Considering your looks,\Nthat's all you could expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.45,0:20:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While you shut yourself up in the bathroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.95,0:20:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanuki-{\i1}san {\i0}is hugging the toilet at the\Nconvenience store getting her comeuppance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Ozu, don't tell\Nme that you and Hanuki-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, don't even joke about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.41,0:20:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She requires a person like the Master far\Nmore than an ordinary individual such as myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.45,0:20:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And yet, for some reason,\NI felt slightly relieved.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:54.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,- collected Kaori-{\i1}san{\i0}. \NThe castella is a reward from Jougasaki-{\i1}san{\i0}.\N- Ozu
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.04,0:21:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder how long Keiko-san had waited?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.54,0:21:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But, it's for the best. I have\Nmaintained my hard-protected chastity.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.91,0:21:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You think I'll let myself be tied\Nto a woman like some shoelace?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've just returned to the starting\Npoint of the game of "Love."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.21,0:21:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This kind of thing's an everyday occurrence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.00,0:21:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I got a castella out of it, so I think it\Nturned out pretty good, all things considered.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.96,0:21:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hang in there! Keep hanging in there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.66,0:21:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I wouldn't mind if I could live\Nmy life again, even just a little bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.33,0:21:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least,\Nstarting from a few hours ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.47,0:21:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
